name: RETURN
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - Bring out your wisdom into the world. This image depicts the ornate collection of wisdom that you've gained in your life so far. Seen from a birds eye view, all of the thresholds you've crossed and the things you've learnt on your journey are there. This card is about your effort and your attention on bringing yourself forward. Push and do whatever it is you need to do to release the flow of your life out into the world. Primal Energy, healing powers and opportunities, promote personal growth rebirth & transformation - censorship is finished the way is open - RETURN

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
